Sazka Board Ties Husak’s Hands in Bankruptcy, Hospodarske Says

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-04-07T06:19:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/sazka-board-ties-husak-s-hands-in-bankruptcy-hospodarske-says.html
Sazka AS’s board of directors barred
Chief Executive Officer Ales Husak from taking any measures
during the Czech lottery company’s bankruptcy without the
board’s approval,  Hospodarske Noviny  reported, citing board
member Roman Jecminek.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
 kchamonikola@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at   gserkin@bloomberg.net  